text: Laxman Singh Rajput (born: 10 August 1992) is an Indian actor who appears in tv serials like Savdhaan India and Jijaji Chhat Per Hain. He has shared the screen with Nawazuddin Siddiqui in Thackeray. He was later seen in Salman Khan's Bharat. ==Television == {| class="wikitable sortable" |- ! Year ! Title ! Role !
